&gt;
&gt; Harverst end: 14.11.2003-12
&gt;
&gt; Harvest time: 67 hours
&gt;
&gt; Total amount of data harvested: 4 GB (compressed), 14 GB (uncompressed)
&gt;
&gt; Compression factor measured to 3.5.
&gt;
&gt; Harvest bandwidth: 14 GB/67 hours = 464 Kbit/sec
&gt;
